&nbsp;The Court of Appeal has confirmed the death sentence imposed on a chef by the Mombasa High Court on February 16 2016 after he was found guilty of raping and murdering a five-year old girl in a hotel on December 31 2012. John Mwazo Machala appealed his conviction and sentence but on Wednesday the court said he was rightly charged, convicted and sentenced.&nbsp; &quot;The prosecution relied on a set of circumstantial evidence to prove that only the appellant had the opportunity to commit the offence.&quot; Said the judges